targets.query: SELECT "Fault"  FROM "Huawei_stat" where 'Status' != null order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT "State1"  FROM "Huawei_stat" where 'Status' != null order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT "State2"  FROM "Huawei_stat" where 'Status' != null order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT  "State3"  FROM "Huawei_stat" where 'Status' != null order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT  "Status"  FROM "Huawei_stat" where 'Status' != null order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT cumulative_sum(integral("power90")) * 0.98 /3600   FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("P_daily") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(previous) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT cumulative_sum(integral("power"))   /3600 * 0.98  FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT cumulative_sum(integral("power10"))   /3600 * 0.98  FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
select integral(prod) /300 from (SELECT mean("P_active")  as prod FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(5m) fill(linear)) GROUP BY time(1m)   fill(previous) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT cumulative_sum(integral("M_P")) /3600 / 1000  FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter  GROUP BY time(1m)  fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT (integral("power90"))   /1800  FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1m) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')

targets.query: SELECT last("PV_P") FROM "Huawei" order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("P_active") FROM "Huawei" order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_P")  / 1000 FROM "Huawei" order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
select p from (SELECT (last("M_P")  /1000  - last("P_active")) as p FROM "Huawei" ) limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
select max(p) from (SELECT last("P_peak") as p FROM "Huawei" WHERE time > now() - 5m) tz('${tzone}')
select max(p) from (SELECT last("P_daily") as p FROM "Huawei" WHERE time > now() - 5m) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT max("P_daily") -  first("P_daily")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE time >= now() - 24h and  time <= now() GROUP BY time(1d) fill(previous) order by time asc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
select cumulative_sum(diff)  as balance from (SELECT first("P_Exp") - first("P_Grid") + first("Adj") as diff FROM "Huawei_daily"  where time > now() -365d   GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0)) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("M_PTot")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE  $timeFilter and  time > now() - 1d and P_daily = 0 and time < now() - 15m GROUP BY time(1d) fill(previous) order by time desc tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_PTot") FROM "Huawei"   GROUP BY  time(1d) fill(null) order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("M_PExp")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE P_daily = 0  GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null) order by time asc tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_PExp") FROM "Huawei"  GROUP BY  time(1d) fill(null) order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("M_PTot")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE  $timeFilter and  time > now() - 1d and P_daily = 0 and time < now() - 15m GROUP BY time(1d) fill(previous) order by time desc tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_PTot") FROM "Huawei"   GROUP BY  time(1d) fill(null) order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("M_PExp")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE P_daily = 0  GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null) order by time asc tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_PExp") FROM "Huawei"  GROUP BY  time(1d) fill(null) order by time desc limit 1 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT  last("P_accum") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_Freq") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT cumulative_sum(integral("M_P")) / 3600 FROM "Huawei" WHERE time > now() - 1h  GROUP BY time(1m) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("P_active") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_P")  / 1000 FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_P")  / 1000 - last("P_active") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("M_A-P")  / 1000 FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("power")  / 1000 FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("power")  / 1000 FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT first("power")  / 1000 FROM "forcast" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(linear) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("P_daily") / ("P_peak") FROM "Huawei_daily" WHERE $timeFilter tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("P_daily") / 8.76 FROM "Huawei_daily" WHERE $timeFilter tz('${tzone}')
select cumulative_sum(diff) * 1000  as balance from (SELECT first("P_Exp") - first("P_Grid") + first("Adj") as diff FROM "Huawei_daily"   GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0)) tz('${tzone}')
select cumulative_sum(diff) as diff from (SELECT  first("P_Grid") as diff FROM "Huawei_daily"   GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0)) tz('${tzone}')
select cumulative_sum(diff) as balance from (SELECT first("P_Exp") as diff FROM "Huawei_daily"   GROUP BY time(1d) fill(0)) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("M_U_AB") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("M_U_BC") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("M_U_CA") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter tz('${tzone}')
SELECT moving_average(mean("M_P"), 5) FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT "M_U_AB", "M_U_CA", "M_U_BC" FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "M_U_AB" > 150 and "M_U_BC" > 150 and "M_U_CA" > 150 tz('${tzone}')

SELECT "M_U_AB", "M_U_CA", "M_U_BC", "M_U_AB_p95", "M_U_CA_p95", "M_U_BC_p95", "M_U_AB_20", "M_U_CA_20", "M_U_BC_20" FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "M_U_AB" > 150 and "M_U_BC" > 150 and "M_U_CA" > 150 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("M_A-U") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "M_A-U" > 50 fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT  ("M_B-U")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "M_B-U" > 50 fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT  "M_C-U" FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "M_C-U" > 50 fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT moving_average(mean("M_P"), 5) FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("U_A-B") FROM "Huawei" WHERE "U_A-B" > 100 and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("U_A") FROM "Huawei" WHERE "U_A" > 50 and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("U_B") FROM "Huawei" WHERE "U_B" > 50 and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("M_A-I") - mean("I_A")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("M_B-I")  - mean("I_A")  FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("M_C-I") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT last("") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter  and "" > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')

select mean(q) from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB")) /  mean("M_U_AB") *100 as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("U_A-B" > 10) AND  ("M_U_AB" > 10)  and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)) GROUP BY time(10m) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT moving_average(mean("I_A"), 10) FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("U_A-B" > 10) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
select mean(q) from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB"))  * mean("I_A") as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("I_A" > 1) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) ) GROUP BY time(10m) tz('${tzone}')

select mean(q) from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB"))  / mean("I_A") * 1000 as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("I_A" > 5) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)) GROUP BY time(10m) tz('${tzone}')
select cumulative_sum(integral(q))/3600 from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB"))  * mean("I_A") as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter  GROUP BY time(1m) fill(0)) GROUP BY time(1h) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("P_active") *1000 FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "P_active" > 0 GROUP BY time(5m) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("P_active") *1000 - mean("M_P") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and 0 < "M_P"  GROUP BY time(5m) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT mean("PV_Un") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and "PV_Un" > 0 GROUP BY time(5m) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("M_Freq") FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter and M_Freq > 5 tz('${tzone}')
SELECT ("Frequency") FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("Frequency" > 5) AND $timeFilter tz('${tzone}')

select mean(q) from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB")) /  mean("M_U_AB") *100 as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("U_A-B" > 10) AND  ("M_U_AB" > 10)  and $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) ) GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT moving_average(mean("I_A"), 10) FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("U_A-B" > 10) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')

select max(q) from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB"))  * mean("I_A") as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("I_A" > 20) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) ) GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')

select max(q) from (SELECT (mean("U_A-B") -  mean("M_U_AB"))  / mean("I_A") * 1000 as q FROM "Huawei" WHERE ("I_A" > 20) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d) fill(null)) GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT min("M_A-I") - mean("I_A") + (min("M_B-I") - mean("I_A")) FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
SELECT min("M_A-I") - mean("I_A") + (min("M_B-I") - mean("I_A")) FROM "Huawei" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null) tz('${tzone}')
